<h2><code>lgColumn</code> directive</h2>
<p>Defines a column template.</p>
<p>Inside the template, a <code>rowData</code> object is accessible in the scope. It contains data from a single record of the data model.
</p>

<h3>Attributes</h3>
<table class="table table-striped">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th>Attribute</th>
			<th>Type</th>
			<th>Description</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>title</td>
			<td>string</td>
			<td>Title of the column (used to render a header if header template is not specified).</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>visible</td>
			<td>boolean</td>
			<td>Determines if a column is rendered.</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<h3>Examples</h3>
<pre highlight="html">
&lt;lg-grid model="myModel"&gt;
	&lt;lg-column title="'Name'"&gt;
		{{ rowData.name }}
	&lt;/lg-column&gt;
	&lt;lg-column title="'Address'"&gt;
		{{ rowData.address }}
	&lt;/lg-column&gt;
&lt;/lg-grid&gt;
</pre>
